Usage: getBlackBoxArea [-help] -cell <string> [-cellUtil] [-macroArea]
                       [-stdCellArea]

-help              # Prints out the command usage
-cell <string>     # Specifies the name of the black box cell
                   # (string, required)
-cellUtil          # Reports the standard cell utilization value for blackbox .
                   # (bool, optional)
-macroArea         # Reports the area of the macros included in the blackbox
                   # area. (bool, optional)
-stdCellArea       # Reports the area of the standard cell included in the
                   # blackbox area. (bool, optional)